 Christianity. Reference Point Press, 2018. {{ISBN|978-1682824610}}\n*Understanding Hinduism. Reference Point Press, 2018. {{ISBN|978-1682824634}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.nardopublishing.com Official Website]\n*{{IMDb name|621368}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Nardo, Don}}\n[[Category:21st-century American historians]]\n[[Category:American male composers]]\n[[Category:21st-century American composers]]\n[[Category:American children's writers]]\n[[Category:Writers from Columbia, Missouri]]\n[[Category:1947 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Worcester State University alumni]]\n[[Category:People from Natick, Massachusetts]]\n[[Category:Musicians from Columbia, Missouri]]\n[[Category:Historians from Massachusetts]]\n[[Category:21st-century American male musicians]]\n", "name_user": "Sancinitoj", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eChildhood and education:Worcester State College is now known as Worcester State University, added clarification and link.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don_Nardo"}
